# Settlement & API

- Keeper settles `open` **and** `locked` markets on `game_finalised` / `statusId=100`.
- Void path must refund full stake via claim; do not mark winners on void markets.
- On-chain `settle` mapping must match `resolveMatchResult` / `resolveTotals`.
- Prefer additive REST routes under `/api`; keep WS events for live fanout only.
- Add or extend unit tests in `packages/shared` when changing resolution.
